{
  "chapter": "001",
  "title": "五帝本纪",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "黄帝简介",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少典</span>的儿子，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">公孙</span>，名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>。他生下来就有神奇的灵性,年幼时就能说话，小时候聪慧敏捷，长大后忠厚机敏，成年后通达明智。"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "轩辕兴起",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>的时候，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">神农氏</span>的势力衰落了。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之间互相侵犯攻打，残暴地欺压<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，而<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">神农氏</span>无力征讨他们。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>就操练<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">干戈</span>武备，用武力征讨那些不来朝贡的诸侯，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都来归附臣服。但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>最为凶暴，没有人能征讨他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">炎帝</span>想要侵犯欺凌<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都归附了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>于是修明德政，整顿军备，调和五气，播种五谷，安抚<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">万民</span>，丈量四方土地，训练<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">熊</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">罴</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">貔貅</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">貙</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>等部族军队，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阪泉之野</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">炎帝</span>交战。经过三次战斗，才实现了自己的志向。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "涿鹿之战",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>作乱，不服从帝的命令。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>就征调<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的军队，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涿鹿之野</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>交战，最终擒获并杀死了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>。"
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "黄帝称帝",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都尊奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，取代<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">神农氏</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>有不顺服的，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>就去征讨；平定后就离开，开山辟路，从未安定居住。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "疆域与治理",
      "text": "向东到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>边，登上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丸山</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岱宗</span>。 向西到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">空桐</span>，登上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸡头</span>山。 向南到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江</span>边，登上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">熊</span>山、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">湘</span>山。 向北驱逐<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">荤粥</span>部族，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">釜山</span>会合诸侯符契，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涿鹿之阿</span>建都。"
    }
  }
}